# ========================================
# CATATAN DEPLOYMENT:
# ========================================
# ‚úÖ File yang AKAN di-commit ke GitHub:
#    - .env.example (template)
#    - package.json, package-lock.json, pnpm-lock.yaml, bun.lock
#    - Source code (.tsx, .ts, .html, .css)
#    - scripts/generate-config.js
#    - Documentation (.md files)
#    - Public assets (images, fonts, etc.)
#
# ‚ùå File yang TIDAK AKAN di-commit:
#    - .env.local (development URLs & secrets)
#    - /node_modules (dependencies - akan di-install otomatis)
#    - /.next (build output - akan di-generate saat deploy)
#    - /public/config.js (generated file)
#    - .vscode, .qodo, .zencoder (IDE & AI tools config)
#    - .vercel (Vercel deployment config)
#
# üöÄ UNTUK DEPLOYMENT VERCEL:
#    1. Push code ke GitHub (file di atas akan otomatis diabaikan)
#    2. Connect repository ke Vercel
#    3. Vercel akan otomatis install dependencies & build
#    4. Set environment variables di Vercel dashboard
# ========================================
